 Privacy Policy — Voice to Text AI                                                                                                                                    
                                                            
  Last updated: March 2026
                                                                                                                                                                       
  What we collect                                                                                                                                                      
  When you use Voice to Text AI, your audio file is temporarily uploaded to OpenAI's Whisper API for transcription. We do not store your audio on our servers. The     
  transcription text and AI summary are stored locally on your device only.                                                                                            
                                                            
  How it's used                                                                                                                                                        
  Audio is sent solely for transcription and summarization. It is not used for training, advertising, or any other purpose.
                                                                                                                                                                       
  Third parties                                                                                                                                                        
  - OpenAI processes your audio for transcription (openai.com/privacy)                                                                                                 
  - Google Play handles payments (payments.google.com/payments/privacynotice)                                                                                          
                                                            
  Data retention                                                                                                                                                       
  Audio files are never stored. Transcription history is stored on your device and can be deleted at any time within the app.
                                                                                                                                                                       
